36
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:31,700
&nbsp;

37
00:01:31,700 --> 00:01:36,100
<font color=yellow>To her mother's way of thinking,
Julie was the perfect child.

38
00:01:36,100 --> 00:01:44,000
