60
00:02:27,600 --> 00:02:34,300
<font color=yellow>There is also a look the parents of not-so-well-behaved
children give to parents like Susan.

61
00:02:34,300 --> 00:02:39,200
<font color=yellow>It says, "welcome to the club."

