144
00:06:56,900 --> 00:07:02,200
&nbsp;

145
00:07:02,200 --> 00:07:04,203
Are you okay?

146
00:07:04,203 --> 00:07:04,900
Come on.

147
00:07:04,900 --> 00:07:07,400
