169
00:08:14,200 --> 00:08:15,600
Right.

170
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,800
They were kissing, huh?

171
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:19,200
Right at my kitchen table.

172
00:08:19,200 --> 00:08:21,200
You must have shocked the hell out of them.

173
