Well, I'm glad you can laugh about this.

174
00:08:23,300 --> 00:08:24,300
They're just being kids.

175
00:08:24,300 --> 00:08:26,700
This is easy for you. You're the father of the boy.

176
00:08:26,700 --> 00:08:29,000
