We'll be moving at the end of the month.

187
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:57,200
You sold the house?

188
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:57,800
Zach.

189
00:08:57,800 --> 00:09:00,200
Why didn't you tell me about this?

190
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:01,600
