197
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:19,500
I wish she'd shot you instead.

198
00:09:19,500 --> 00:09:26,400
&nbsp;

199
00:09:26,400 --> 00:09:29,100
So you're moving.

200
00:09:29,100 --> 00:09:29,300
&nbsp;

