245
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:42,900
I will fire my lawyer tomorrow. Just give me the word.

246
00:11:42,900 --> 00:11:45,300
Sweetie, I think it's too late.

247
00:11:45,300 --> 00:11:46,000
Why?

248
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:48,400
Because you were unfaithful.

249
00:11:48,400 --> 00:11:51,400
